	<level>
	  <content>
	    <p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:#FF0000">This judgment was delivered in private. The judge has given leave for this version of the judgment to be published on condition that (irrespective of what is contained in the judgment) in any published version of the judgment the anonymity of all parties must be strictly preserved. All persons, including representatives of the media, must ensure that this condition is strictly complied with. Failure to do so will be a contempt of court.</span></p>
	  </content>
	</level>
	<level>
	  <content>
	    <p style="text-align:right"><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:12pt">Neutral Citation Number: <ref href="https://caselaw.nationalarchives.gov.uk/ewcop/2022/29" uk:canonical="[2022] EWCOP 29" uk:isNeutral="true" uk:origin="TNA" uk:type="case" uk:year="2022">[2022] EWCOP 29</ref></span></p>
	  </content>
